snippet.textDisplay:
Even though Guy was the last man standing, I'm going to personally call this match a draw. Guy only managed to properly beat All Might due to the Eighth Gate, which is so brutal that it cripples him afterwards. Considering Naruto isn't around to heal him, though, this is a literal death sentence for him. Since they were both dead by the end of it, I view it as a tie; if we're talking strictly last man standing stuff and ignoring the recoil, then Guy did actually score the win.
My logic is just that a victory is only truly obtained if you live long enough to properly walk away from it; a few seconds isn't enough to me.
